descript.abstract: StreetNames for TRANSPO.SNDSEG, TRANSPO.MAF and CADASTRAL.LEGAL_LN
descript.purpose: Streetname reference for the Street Network Database (SND) and Master Address File (MAF). Contains standardized streetname components and alternative geocoding configurations for all streetnames within SND and MAF.
descript.supplinf: TRANSPO.STNAME is a list of street names: past and present, current and no longer in use, including variations on spelling. It also includes names of ramps and bridges that are not designated by ordinance.

Street Type - The type of street, such as Drive, Street, Avenue, Lane, etc.
